PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RUTH RAMSDEN-WOOD of Calgary, Alberta, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Civilization to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of A. Webster Macdonald.
